      • edit

        public void edit()
        Description copied from interface: LinphoneFriend
        Starts editing a friend configuration.
        Because friend configuration must be consistent, applications MUST call LinphoneFriend.edit() before doing any attempts to modify friend configuration (such as address or subscription policy and so on). Once the modifications are done, then the application must call LinphoneFriend.done() to commit the changes.
        Specified by:
        edit in interface LinphoneFriend
